Package gui

Class Composite

java.lang.Object
gui.Composite
All Implemented Interfaces:
Component
public class Composite
extends java.lang.Object
implements Component
Create a simple GUI that includes: - a text field and a button that allows the user to enter numbers. - a button that allows the user to clear all entered numbers. - a panel with labels and text fields for count, median, and mean. - a text area that shows all numbers. For the MVC architecture pattern, those are the views and controllers.
